data.description: Welcome Home! Nestled in the picturesque Heather Hill neighborhood of Flossmoor, your new home is a haven of comfort and style. A grand entrance welcomes you with double doors, setting the tone for the elegance and warmth that resides within.  Your new Heather Hill home in Flossmoor is a sanctuary of comfort and elegance. The grand double-door entry sets the stage for a welcoming ambiance. With 4 spacious bedrooms, including a master bedroom featuring an ensuite bathroom and abundant closet space throughout, luxury meets practicality seamlessly.    The heart of this home radiates warmth with a wood-burning fireplace gracing the cozy family room. An adjoining dining room and a charming eat-in kitchen create perfect spaces for gatherings and culinary delights. Step outside to discover an inviting deck overlooking a vast yard, ideal for enjoying outdoor moments.    A well-appointed basement adds to the allure, housing a recreational room equipped with a screen for immersive movie experiences. The convenience of a laundry unit in the basement ensures effortless chores.    To complete this picture-perfect setting, a two-car garage stands ready to shelter your vehicles and provide extra storage space. Welcome to your new haven in Heather Hill, where comfort, functionality, and relaxation harmoniously intertwine.    The seller is offering a one year Home Warranty as well as closing credit in this As-Is Sale.
